data.name: Tn-Core-webserver
data.description: Help files and sample data for the Tn-Core webserver. The code supporting the web server is also included.

evidence: "The Tn-Core webserver is a web-based implementation of one of the main functionalities of Tn-Core: extraction of a context-specific core metabolic network on the basis of TnSeq data. The webserver returns the core metabolic network in two formats..." (describes an end-user web application performing analyses).

"If you have questions about the use of the Tn-Core webserver, please send inquiries to George diCenzo... or Marco Fondi..." (points to individual researchers rather than an institution or community project).

"Additionally, this repository contains a folder with five files for use as sample data to test the Tn-Core webserver." (indicates distribution via the repository itself; no mention of package managers, containers, or binaries).
